TITLE: Configuring Select2 with AJAX in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: JavaScript code to initialize Select2 with AJAX support, using GitHub's API as an example data source.
SOURCE: https://github.com/select2/select2/blob/develop/docs/pages/06.data-sources/02.ajax/docs.md#2025-04-22_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
$('.js-data-example-ajax').select2({
  ajax: {
    url: 'https://api.github.com/search/repositories',
    dataType: 'json'
    // Additional AJAX parameters go here; see the end of this chapter for the full code of this example
  }
});
```

----------------------------------------

TITLE: Implementing Pagination in Select2 AJAX Requests
DESCRIPTION: JavaScript code demonstrating how to implement pagination for AJAX requests in Select2.
SOURCE: https://github.com/select2/select2/blob/develop/docs/pages/06.data-sources/02.ajax/docs.md#2025-04-22_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
$('#mySelect2').select2({
  ajax: {
    url: 'https://api.github.com/search/repositories',
    data: function (params) {
      var query = {
        search: params.term,
        page: params.page || 1
      }

      // Query parameters will be ?search=[term]&page=[page]
      return query;
    }
  }
});
```

