TITLE: Setting Default Values for AJAX-populated Select2
DESCRIPTION: HTML markup showing how to set a pre-selected default value for a Select2 control that uses AJAX data.
SOURCE: https://github.com/select2/select2/blob/develop/docs/pages/06.data-sources/02.ajax/docs.md#2025-04-22_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: html
CODE:
```
<select class="js-example-data-ajax form-control">
  <option value="3620194" selected="selected">select2/select2</option>
</select>
```

